Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧 你是饿坏了吧\NThere. You were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:30.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第三卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:37.37,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《农事诗》: 维吉尔(古罗马诗人)农业诗篇 论耕作与农事纷争】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）...终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,继续念\NRepeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NGood day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘好\NGood day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你来休兰农场来做什么？\NWhat brings you to Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里教孩子\NI'm tutoring the boys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,教拉丁的先生啊\NThe Latin tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过你\NI've heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来这园里干什么？\NWhat brought you into the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就随口问问 教书先生\NIt's just a question, master tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我 那个...\NYes, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是出来透透气 而且...\NI suppose the air was fresh out here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我看到你带着只鸟\Nuh, I saw you with your bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是只鹰 - 哦\N- It's a hawk. - Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能上前看看吗？\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别凑太近\NDon't get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他没见过你\NHe doesn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 小家伙\NHello, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哈哈哈\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢你\NHe likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\NWhat is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别打听\NI shan't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就打听\NYou shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不说\NI shan't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会说的 - 我不会\N- You shall. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等我亲你时你就会说了\NYou'll tell me when we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫安妮丝\NMy name is Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你家哪儿的？\NWhere are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我说错话了吗？\NHave I said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊？ - 没有\N- Huh? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不知道我是谁 - 等下 我能去你...\N- You don't know who I am. - Wait, I wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你别再来找我了\NYou can't see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了？\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我下地帮巴塞洛缪\NI was in the field helping Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小羊崽病了\NA newborn lamb is unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我也去地里了\NWell, I... I went to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可没见你啊\NI did not see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实在那儿 巴塞洛缪哥 你给她说说\NWell, I was there. Tell her, Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她确实在那里\NShe was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过新来的拉丁先生吗？\NHave you seen the new Latin tutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是皮匠的儿子\NThe glover's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们说他上着上着课跑掉了 就再没回来\NThe boys said he just ran out, never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来教书还债的\NHe was supposed to give them lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还他父亲的债\Nto pay off his father's debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过他\NI haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 早该料到\NWell, should've known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,父子都一个德行\NLike father, like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩可是咱们教区最美的姑娘\NYou know, I do believe you are the prettiest girls in the parish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 将来...\N- We are. - One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,会有许多人上门提亲 我亲自把关\NI shall have my wits about me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,准把你们嫁个好人家\Nfor all the suitors that will come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝是大姐 还轮不到我们\NAgnes is the eldest. She'll marry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她成天往树林里跑 像个流浪女\NShe will not if she keeps running off to the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会娶她？\Nlike a gypsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们说... - 你去哪儿了?\N- When they said... - Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都等你好几个钟头了\NWe were expecting you hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在... - 说啊\N- I was... - Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在忙事儿\NI was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\NSit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快坐下吧\NSit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,饭菜都凉了\NYour supper's near cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别闹 别闹 - 别抢\N- Uh, boys, boys! - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住手 - 大家都有份 别抢\N- Stop. - There's enough for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰农场那边教得怎么样？\NHow go the lessons at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孩子不是读书的料\NThose boys are no scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就纳闷 他们读书有啥用 - 嗯\N- I wonder at the notion of all that learning. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,注定务农的孩子学拉丁文？\NLatin for boys who will be naught but sheep farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 用来装模做样吗？ - 不 不 不\N- It is the putting on of airs. - No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 够了 - 都给你 吉尔伯特\N- That will do! - All right, Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,听你娘的 都有份 别争\NYou heard your mother. There's enough for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你说休兰那帮孩子不好\NYou speak ill of the boys at Hewlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是读书的料”\N"They're no scholars."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可我跟你说 他们将来...\NBut I tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,比你更像个男子汉\Nthey'll ever be more of a man than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人家将来有正经活 你没有\NThey are put to honest work, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没出息 没手艺 只会装模做样\NUseless, tradeless, your fancy airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,读那么多书\NAll that education,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一点用都没有\Nnot an ounce of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我这没出息的去教书\NI'm tutoring those boys to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是替你还那户人家的债吗？\Nyour debts to that family, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠休兰家那么多债\NYour immeasurable amount of debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我... 住手\NDidn't I help you... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰那边其他人\NWhat of the rest of the family at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你都见过吗？\NHave you met them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只见过那户的母亲\NThe mother only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那大女儿没见到吗？ - 没有\N- Not the eldest daughter? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都说 那姑娘是森林巫婆的后代 \NIt is said the girl is the child of a forest witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我就见过 她独自走在山路上\NI've seen her, wandering the back roads alone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,臂上还有只鹰\Nwith a hawk on her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰那儿还有鹰？\NA hawk at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,传言说她每次进林都是一个人带着那只鹰\NThey say she takes him to the forest with her unaccompanied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗 伊莱莎？\NYeah, but are you certain, Eliza?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那拿着鹰的是长女 不是仆人？\NThe eldest daughter keeps a hawk, not a servant girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是仆人 我确定\NYes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑这来干什么？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,送个东西给你\NBrought you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...\NIt's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给你那只鸟的新手套\Nit's a new glove for your bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有手套\NI have a glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 别跑\NAgnes, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我认出你了\NI know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 我是谁？\NWho am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不算了解你 只是听到些传言...\NWell, I... I don't know you, but I've heard things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,说我是森林巫婆的女儿？\NI'm the daughter of a forest witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 村里这么说 但我 我不在意...\NYes. People say that, but I-I don't care...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是我娘的女儿\NI am my mother's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从她那儿学的本事多着呢\NI've learnt many things from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞎看什么？\NWhat are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看你 - 为什么？\N- You. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因... - 你这教书的 不该能言善辩吗？\N- I... - I thought you were a man of words, master tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还难住你了？ - 只是...\N- Are you not? - Jus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时很难直接跟人说话\NSpeaking with people is sometimes difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就讲个故事吧\NWell, tell me a story, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 讲故事？ - 对\N- A story? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想听什么故事？\NWhat story would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,起码能打动你自己的故事\NSomething that moves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道俄耳甫斯和欧律狄刻的故事吗？\NDo you know the story of Orpheus and Eurydice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.74,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 古希腊神话】
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯这个男人\NOrpheus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有着天赋异禀的音乐才能\Na man of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有着天籁般的嗓音\NHe has this exquisite voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他弹那种七弦里拉 是...\NHis playing of the kithara, which is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是类似竖琴的乐器\Nis-is a harp-like lyre,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,声音美得妙不可言\Nis so divine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,连天上的鸟儿 地...\Nbirds, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,地上的走兽 甚 甚至石头和树\Nthe beasts, e-even the stones and the trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都能被他的音乐打动随之起舞\Nthey all moved to the rhythm of his music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,后来 俄耳甫斯爱上了一位美丽的山林少女 叫欧律狄刻\NNow, Orpheus falls in love with this beautiful nymph, Eurydice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和山林少女刚结完婚\NSoon after their marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她就被毒蛇咬了\NEurydice's bitten by a viper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,毒素在她体内迅速扩散\Nand poison courses through her body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她就此身亡\Nand she's killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯悲痛欲绝\NAnd Orpheus, filled with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下到冥府想要将她带回\Njourneys to the underworld to take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他用琴声迷住了守门的三头犬 刻耳柏洛斯\NHe charms this three-headed dog, Cerberus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至感动了冥王哈得斯 最终...\NHe beguiles Hades until finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,冥王同意了\N...he's allowed to take his love back with him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,允许把这名女子带回人间 但...\Nto the world of the living but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一个条件\N...under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么条件？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这名女子必须跟在他身后\NShe must follow behind him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而他绝对不能回头看\Nand he must not turn around to look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 他们开始往人间走\NNow, as they begin their ascent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯却听不见他妻子的脚步声\NOrpheus can't hear her footsteps, so he listens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,于是他听啊 听啊 一直听\N...and listens and listens and listens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他只听得见自己的心跳\NBut all he can hear is the sound of his heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,余下的只有沉寂\NAnd the rest is silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当他快到冥门出口时\NAnd as he approaches the gates of the underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他忍不住了\N...he can't contain himself any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他回头去看妻子 然后妻子...\NHe turns around to look at her, and she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,永远被困在冥府里了\N...trapped in the underworld forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好故事\NThat was a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗？\NDid you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\NRemember, mugwort, what you brought to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:43.85,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《九草咒》: 古英语药咒 列九种草药以驱毒治疫】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德 传颂至今\Nwhat you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\NYou're called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\NYou defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\Nyou defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\Nyou defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,车前草者 草之母也\NAnd you, waybread, plant mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,根植东方 性禀刚毅\Nyou're open to the east yet mighty within.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,遭车碾而不折 遇众踏而复起\NCarts creeped over you, women rode over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,刚柔相济 疗人间之疾苦\NYou withstood it all, and you pushed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的能靠摸一个人的手\NIs it true that you know everything about a person
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看透一切吗？\Nby touching them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,并非全部\NNot everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸我时你看到了什么？\NWhen you touched me here, what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见了一幅画面\NI saw a landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一幅画？ - 嗯\N- You saw a landscape? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,空洞 黑洞 裂口\NSpaces, caves, cliff tops,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,暗道和深海\Ntunnels and oceans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,深不见底 一片漆黑的虚空\Nthis deep, dark, black void,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,未知的国度\Nundiscovered countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）天道有常 宿命有律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.30,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第一卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）万物难逃衰落之数 消亡乃其必然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）天道有常 宿命有律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）万物难逃衰落之数 消亡乃其必然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了...\NShe speaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了 她说话了\NShe speaks, she speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢\NBut, soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那窗户透出来的是什么光？\Nwhat light through yonder window breaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是东方 朱丽叶就是太阳...\NIt is the east, and Juliet is the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,赶走那....\N...and kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嫉妒的月亮\N...the envious moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.97,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在创作《罗密欧与朱丽叶》第二幕第二场】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你成亲\NI wish to be handfasted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我 我必须和你成亲\NNo, I... I must be handfasted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,非你不可\NNo one else will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去跟你继母和你哥哥说\NI-I will speak with your stepmother and your brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,估计他们不会答应\Nand of course they will not agree, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不管行不行就这么定了 不能等了\NI don't care because I have no talent for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是私定终身\NI cannot abide waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那你父母怎么办？\NWhat about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们绝不会答应的\NYour parents will never agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等 等下\NWait. Wait. W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跑不掉了 - 别\N- No! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手套\NMy glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我母亲留给我的 - 哦\N- This is my mother's glove. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她源于丛林\NShe came out of the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就像她的母亲一样\N...like her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,像她母亲的母亲一样\Nand her mother before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我家族女人能看到些...\NThe women in my family see things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别人看不到的东西\N...that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\NRemember, mugwort,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德 传颂至今\Nwhat you brought to pass, what you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\NYou're called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\NYou defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\Nyou defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\Nyou defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,巴塞洛缪 会好的\NBartholomew, it will heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会留疤吗？\NWill it make a scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会 但并非坏事\NIt may. That's no bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,听见了么？\NDo you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,留心你的梦 安妮丝\NYou must pay attention to your dreams, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,梦永远会指引你\NThey will always guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们好 - 你也好\N- Good day. - Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你怎么在...\NAgnes, what's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这儿？\Nwhat's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她母亲把她逐出家门了\NHer mother has banished her from their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我生母 而且...\NShe's not my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我家那房子归我哥哥巴塞洛缪\NThe house belongs to my brother, Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是自愿离开的\NI chose to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她有身孕了\NShe's with child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还说孩子是你的\NSays it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗？真是你的吗？ - 呃...\N- Is it? Yours? - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她肚子里的孩子 是你弄的吗？\NThe child in her belly, did you put it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们已经私定了 娘 - 休想\N- We are handfasted, Mother. - We will never allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这有什么错啊 - 没我们的同意\N- There is no sin in it. - I'm afraid you will need
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你成不了亲的 - 这有什么错啊\N- our consent, and we will... - There is no sin in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们决不允许这桩婚事 - 行 行\N- ...we will never give it, ever! - All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你被她蛊惑了 - 不是的\N- You've been bewitched. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿你当水手送命 也别娶这个巫婆\NI'd rather you went to sea than marry this wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不必这样\NThere's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他们两厢情愿 这事好解决\NI have no doubt we can come to an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰 - 安静 女人\N- John. - Hush, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定想在教堂里\NI am certain you are eager
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你妹妹出嫁吧\Nto see your sister before the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定想现在\NI'm certain you'd rather not see your boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,控告你儿子奸淫\Ndragged before the bawdy court.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要闹成那样\NThere's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都已经私定了\NThey said they are handfasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁不嫁由我说了算\NOnly if I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁给那白面书生到底有啥好处？他有什么用\NBut why marry a pasty-faced scholar? What use is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他的内心比我见过的任何人都深邃\NHe's got more inside of him than any man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人心是会变的\NEverything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你也不例外\NYou. You will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心已经变了\NI'm already changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,里头太静了\NIt's too quiet in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿里头？\NIn where?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们家\NThat house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,记得我们害怕迷茫时 娘怎么劝咱的吗？\NWhat would our mother say to us if we were afraid or uncertain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要敞开心扉\NTo live with our hearts open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫它躲在黑暗里\NTo shut it not in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要转向太阳 去拥抱那温暖\Nbut to turn it to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他爱的是我本色 不图我变成谁\NHe loves me for what I am, not what I ought to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就嫁给他吧\NThen marry him you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\NRemember, mugwort...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来 说跟我一起说 一起说\NSay it with me. Say it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德\NWhat you brought to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,传颂至今\Nwhat you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\NYou are called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\NYou defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\Nyou defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.85,0:24:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\Nyou defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.18,0:25:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.73,0:27:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.49,0:29:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.11,0:29:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看 看那光 那是火\NLook. Look at that. Look at the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.98,0:29:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 那是什么啊\NMmm, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.39,0:29:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是小狗叼进来的东西\NThe doggy dragged something in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快看\NThere's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.82,0:29:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.04,0:29:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你爹回来了\NDaddy's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.11,0:29:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.15,0:30:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,针脚要小一点\NStitches need to be smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.26,0:30:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再小 再小一点\NM-Much smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.46,0:30:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哼\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.68,0:30:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没出息\NUseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.37,0:30:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再小点\NOkay, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.28,0:30:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再小点\Nsmaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.30,0:30:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿？ - 我要出去\N- Where are you going? - I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.80,0:30:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,回去干活\NGet back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.04,0:30:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后一次打我\NThat was the last time you will ever hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.65,0:30:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.18,0:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？ - 明白\N- Do you understand?! - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.37,0:31:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爱人 该睡觉了\NMy love, you should come back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在写什么？\NWhat are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.11,0:31:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不值一提\NNothing of note.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.12,0:31:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,总有值得称道的地方\NIt's never nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.67,0:31:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还没写好呢\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.31,0:31:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许写完会好...\NPerhaps when it's finished, it will...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.29,0:31:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\NPerhaps when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.68,0:31:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,念给我听听吧\NWhy don't you read me what you've written?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.09,0:31:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 这还没...\NA-Agnes, it's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.63,0:31:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还没写好呢\NIt-It's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.92,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没写好\NIt's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.96,0:31:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别敲了 吵醒孩子了\NStop it. You'll wake the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.55,0:31:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.54,0:32:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不哭 不哭\NNo. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.47,0:32:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.53,0:32:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝多了\NI've had too much, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 我喝多了\NAgnes, I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.16,0:32:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝...\NI've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.51,0:32:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝的太多了\NI've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.41,0:32:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.15,0:32:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么心事吗？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.03,0:32:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你的手看看\NGive me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.71,0:32:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 别 别 别\NPl-Pl-Please, please, please, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.75,0:32:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 求你了 别\Nplease, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怕我看见什么吗？ - 求你了 别\N- What are you afraid I will see? - Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.22,0:32:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕我将来会伤害你\NThat I am a violent and dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.36,0:32:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 你不是那样的人\NNo, you are none of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.77,0:32:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么能肯定？ - 你是个好人 你是个...\N- How do you know? - You're a good man. You're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.20,0:32:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\NYou are a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.74,0:33:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\NYou're a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.04,0:33:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是后悔跟我结婚了吗？\NIs it that you wish that we never wed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.95,0:33:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能说出这种话？\NHow could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.24,0:33:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能说出这种话？\NHow could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.62,0:33:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着就是为了你和苏珊娜\NYou and Susanna are all that I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.89,0:33:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着就是为了你们\NAll that I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.70,0:33:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那到底怎么回事？ - 是...\N- What is it, then? - This...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.91,0:33:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 把手给我 - 停下\N- Here. Look at me. - Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.88,0:33:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,停 停 求你停下 停 停 停\NStop, stop. Please, please, please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.76,0:33:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.31,0:33:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 听着 听我说\NListen. Listen. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.37,0:33:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷失了\NI'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.92,0:33:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不...\NI've lost my...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.10,0:33:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到方向了\NI've lost my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.93,0:34:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要 我需要静下心好好写作 安妮丝\NI just need to-- uh, Agnes, I just need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.82,0:34:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他都睡不着觉 \NHe's not sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他对你发过火了吗？ - 没有\N- Has he ever lost his temper with you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.23,0:34:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要是他对你动手.... - 没有 他从没那样 从没那样\N- If he raises a hand... - No, he has never. He's never.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.93,0:34:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是为自己懊恼\N He's angry with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.23,0:34:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,心里难受得要命\NHe's sick with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.45,0:34:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\NHe's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.72,0:34:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好丈夫 也是个好父亲\NHe's a good husband, he's a good father,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.15,0:34:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但他还需要更多\Nbut he n-needs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.05,0:34:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经有了家和你 还能需要什么？\NWhat could he possibly need other than his family and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.54,0:34:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他已经有了你 - 他需要去伦敦\N- He has you. - He needs to go to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.92,0:34:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伦敦？ - 是的\N- London? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥去伦敦？ \NWhy London?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.72,0:34:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为伦敦汇聚天下\NBecause London is where the whole world gathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.76,0:34:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定能把他爹的手艺带去发扬光大\NPerhaps he could extend his father's business there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.96,0:34:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎 你又冲动了 - 谁知道他将来会怎样\N- Oh, you're being hasty again. - Who knows what he may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.60,0:34:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是冲动 他需要更多\NI'm not being hasty. He needs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.31,0:34:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他只是太闲了 - 他不该呆这小地方\N- Well, he needs proper work. - He's not of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.27,0:34:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给他找个活儿忙起来\NThe man needs proper work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.66,0:34:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这小地方能有什么出路？ -  他不能就这么跑掉\N- What's in this little town? - He can't just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.14,0:34:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这小日子 这小地方\NThis little life? This little thing, it'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.94,0:34:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会逼疯他的\N...crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.26,0:34:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他得离他爹远点\NHe needs distance from his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.15,0:34:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他一起去伦敦吗？\NAnd you would go with him to London?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.43,0:34:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等他安顿好再说\NNo, I'll wait until he's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.32,0:34:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,马上家里就会多一口人\NThere'll be more of us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.86,0:34:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 又怀上了？ - 是的\N- Another child? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.80,0:34:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,夏末时候生\NBy summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.17,0:35:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在更不能把他送走了\NThen now is not the time to send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.77,0:35:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我会失去他的\NI'll lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.07,0:35:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在失去他了\NI'm already losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.52,0:35:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要是送他走 就彻底失去他了\NYou'll lose him if you send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.64,0:35:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不会的 我肯定我俩的爱能维系得住\NNo, I know, I know that our love will keep us steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.15,0:35:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 替我跟他爹说说吧\NPlease. Will you speak to his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.82,0:35:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你跟他提去伦敦的事 他会听你的\NHe'll listen to you if you suggest him going to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.52,0:35:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我得找个住处\NI should find lodgings.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.91,0:35:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最好靠河的 离河边皮革场近点\NBe near the river, close to the tanneries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.44,0:35:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说那河水很急\NBut I'm told that the currents in the river are dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.13,0:35:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,过河要请有经验的船夫\Nand that you must engage an experienced boatman
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.21,0:35:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每次过河我都照办\Nevery time you cross, and I'll be certain to do that every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.53,0:35:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.11,0:35:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会时时想念你和苏珊娜\NAnd I will think of you and Susanna
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.73,0:35:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一刻也不会忘了你们\Nwith every passing moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.26,0:35:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给咱们找个好住处\NAnd I will find us lodgings in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.84,0:35:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候在伦敦团聚\Nand we shall all be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.83,0:35:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没预见出是男孩还是女孩吗？\NDo you still not know if it's a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.07,0:35:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.21,0:35:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也说不清为什么\NDon't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说过会有两个孩子陪你到最后吗？\NHave you not said that you would always have two children?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.48,0:35:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.08,0:36:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,临终前会有两个孩子在身边\NTwo children at my deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.90,0:36:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个能陪你到最后的人来了\NWell, then, here is the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.96,0:36:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们就别道别了 - 好\N- We won't say goodbye. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.91,0:36:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别磨蹭了 快走吧\NYou get-- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.42,0:37:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要出门吗？ - 不是 我只是...\N- You going somewhere? - No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.99,0:37:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我要去湖边走走...\NYes, I'm going to the lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.94,0:37:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不许进森林\NYou're not going to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.61,0:37:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我非去不可 - 不 你不许去 吉尔伯特快来\N- I must. - No, you must not. Gilbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.03,0:37:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你得让我去那里\NYou... you have to let me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.08,0:37:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必须让我走 - 听我说 安妮丝\N- Let me go there! - Listen Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.10,0:37:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你得放我去 - 河堤已经决口了\N- You must let me go! - The river has burst its banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.64,0:37:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我去 - 外面很危险\N- Let me! - There is no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.88,0:37:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 根本没路去森林那边 - 放我走 不要\N- There's no way to get to the forest. - Let me! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.73,0:37:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们都为你准备好了 - 我孩子\N- We have everything ready for you. - My baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.38,0:37:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我 我孩子\NNo, my-my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.47,0:37:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.21,0:37:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,生不出来\NIt isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.45,0:37:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法在这屋里生孩子\NI will not have my baby in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.90,0:37:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没法在这屋\NNot in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.51,0:37:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没法\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.11,0:37:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,河水\NThe river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 使劲儿 使劲儿 使劲儿 - 不 不 不\N- Hush, hush, hush, hush. Hush. - No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.76,0:37:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他说要住河边\NHe spoke about the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.99,0:38:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,河很危险 他可能会被冲走\NThe river is dangerous. He may be swept downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.35,0:38:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝\NAgnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.71,0:38:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝 他一切安好\NAgnes. Agnes, all is well with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.75,0:38:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道忘了他最近的信吗？\NDo you not recall his last letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.93,0:38:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫了\NStop the screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.07,0:38:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,会把整村人都吵醒的\NYou'll wake the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.28,0:38:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他语气...\NHe sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.41,0:38:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他语气不对\NHe sounded different.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.03,0:38:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他带来的是好消息\NNo, he had good news for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.24,0:38:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 剧院 - 剧院\N- The theater. - Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.54,0:38:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他和剧团定下来了\NHe has a contract with the players
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.99,0:38:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做剧院用的手套 - 剧院\N- to make gloves for the theater. - the theater
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.55,0:38:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 使劲儿\NAgnes, hush now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.47,0:38:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,使劲儿 使劲儿 使劲儿\NHush. Hush. Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.87,0:38:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,用力 用力\NBear down. Bear down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.14,0:38:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 来了\NAh! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.22,0:38:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出来了 - 是个男孩\N- There we go. - It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.08,0:38:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\NThere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.39,0:38:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子 乖孩子\NGood boy. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩\NIt's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.29,0:38:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩\NIt's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.66,0:38:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\NMy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.52,0:38:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.36,0:39:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？怎么了？\NWhat is it? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.50,0:39:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她又要生了\NShe's starting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.69,0:39:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 姑娘啊 你怀的是双胞胎 - 来 伊莱莎\N- You're having twins, my girl. - Come on, Eliza.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.89,0:39:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快 抱着他\NHere. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.38,0:39:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,抱好\NTake him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.67,0:39:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.10,0:39:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我临终前会有两个孩子在身边\NTwo standing at my deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.97,0:39:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为...\NI always believed that it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.90,0:39:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以为是长大的孩子\Nthat they would be my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.94,0:39:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我...\NAnd now...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.67,0:39:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 原来就是你们俩\Nnow I see it will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.43,0:39:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,得把你扶到产凳上\NWe need to get you to the stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.78,0:39:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快生了 要生了\NIt's coming. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.16,0:39:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 来 来 起来 起来\N- No. - Come on. Come on up. Up, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别 我 我不行\NPlease. I can't... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.45,0:39:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.68,0:39:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 - 我不该...\N- Go. - I should never have...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.72,0:39:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了...\NI can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.74,0:39:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺不过去了\NI can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.19,0:40:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄错了 我弄错了\NI got it wrong. I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.08,0:40:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄错...\NI got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.38,0:40:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他不在\NHe... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.82,0:40:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他不在这里\NHe's... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.08,0:40:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你能行的\NAgnes, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.38,0:40:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须行\Nand you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\NI cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.02,0:40:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.38,0:40:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你能行的\NYou can...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.17,0:40:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你会挺过去的\Nand you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.06,0:40:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫就在这间屋里出生\NYour husband was born here in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.44,0:40:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那窗边 第一次呼吸\NHe took his first breath there by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.19,0:40:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 保住孩子\NPlease let this child live.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.08,0:40:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一定保孩子 一定\NLet this child live. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让他....\NWill you let him...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.63,0:40:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让他回到家后能有孩子陪他\NLet him come back and be with his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.50,0:40:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.96,0:40:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让他对我留个好念想\NLet him think kindly of me always.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.45,0:40:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,记着我\NRemember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.07,0:40:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.36,0:40:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.70,0:41:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘？\NMum?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.39,0:41:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她没抗住\NJust too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.19,0:41:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她承受了很大的痛苦\NShe was in too much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.36,0:41:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太可怜了\NI mean, poor woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.70,0:41:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越痛 她承受不住了\NShe just got weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.96,0:41:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候命就是这样\NI mean, that's just the way of it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.48,0:41:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她 她大概早就知道这一刻了\NShe-she must have known the end was nigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.22,0:41:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别跟孩子提起她了\NBest not speak of her to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.10,0:41:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,再娶一个吧\NSafer with a different mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.60,0:41:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子都还小\NSo young.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.64,0:41:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兴许能忘掉\NThey may not remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.74,0:41:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘啊 - 安妮丝 安妮丝\N- Mum! - Agnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.51,0:41:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘啊 不 - 不 不 安妮丝\N- Mama, no! - No, no. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.46,0:41:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子 孩子\NChild. Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.85,0:41:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘 不要 - 不 不 孩子 孩子 不行\N- Mummy, no! - No, no, no. Ch-Ch-Ch-- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.25,0:41:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放开我 - 不行\N- No! - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.47,0:41:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 让我见娘 - 不 不\N- No, let me see her! - No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.56,0:41:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要见娘 - 不\N- Let me see her! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.24,0:41:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 娘\NNo, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.88,0:41:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安妮丝 - 不\N- Agnes. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.95,0:41:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,娘 我要我娘 我要我娘\NMum. I want, I want my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.81,0:41:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我娘啊...\NI want my mum...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.65,0:42:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 是个女孩\NOh! Here we go! It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是个女孩 她...\NIt's a girl. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.91,0:42:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等... - 怎么了？\N- It's... Wait. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.59,0:42:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.85,0:42:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么不哭？\NWhy is she not crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.90,0:42:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么不哭？\NWhy is she not crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.79,0:42:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她没活过来\NShe lives not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.65,0:42:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我抱抱\NLet me have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.67,0:42:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这不吉利\NYou should not look upon her. It's bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.49,0:42:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把她给我\NGive her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.48,0:42:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把她安葬妥当的\NI'll make sure it gets a decent burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.68,0:42:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把我孩子给我\NGive me my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.69,0:42:49.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【双胞胎: 当时双胞胎被视为怪异现象和不祥征兆】
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.11,0:42:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子啊\NMy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.62,0:42:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你有个儿子\NAgnes, you have a baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.24,0:43:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他抱来 你可以喂他\NLet me bring him to you, and you may feed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.98,0:43:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩已经去了天国\NThe girl has gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.98,0:43:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会去天国的\NShe's not gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.86,0:43:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲去世那晚我发过誓\NI made a vow the night my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.25,0:43:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去你们的教堂 但别指望我开口说什么\NI will go to your church, but I shan't say a word there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.25,0:43:21.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 当时无宗教自由 故以含蓄方式表达不信教】
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.34,0:44:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了 太好了\NYes. Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.72,0:44:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的\NYou will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.56,0:44:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的\NYou will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.53,0:44:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护你到底 绝不放手\NI will make sure nothing ever takes you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.63,0:44:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么都找不到\NI actually couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.00,0:44:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.29,0:45:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.61,0:45:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.94,0:45:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,找到帽子了\NI found my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.18,0:45:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来 对\NOkay. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.47,0:45:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来 转过去 转过去\NOkay, take that side. Take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.70,0:45:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.14,0:45:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后系好\NAnd put it around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.55,0:45:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,完美\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.25,0:45:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎呀 - 我来吧\N- Ooh. Sorry. - Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.57,0:45:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,挡到我脸了\NIt's down my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.09,0:45:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我学“我是哈姆奈特” - “我是哈姆奈特”\N- I'm Hamnet. - I'm Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.13,0:45:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我是珠迪丝” - “我是珠迪丝”\N- I'm Judith. - I'm Judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.88,0:46:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,屋里不准跑\NThere will be no running in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.46,0:46:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要举止端正 要像...\NConduct yourselves, please, as...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.20,0:46:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,淑女与绅士\Ngentlewomen and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.39,0:46:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪儿？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.82,0:46:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对 他来了 他来了\NYeah. He's-he's coming. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.50,0:46:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.59,0:46:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.48,0:46:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一看就知道他俩对调了衣服\NWe all know they've swapped clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.63,0:46:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们什么时候揭穿？\NHow long are we going to pretend we don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.42,0:46:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们继续演 咱们就不揭穿\NWe'll pretend for as long as they think they're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.64,0:46:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.25,0:46:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,爹 能再教我下\NFather, will you help me with the Greek passage
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.08,0:46:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天那段希腊文吗？\Nfrom yesterday's lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.77,0:46:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 你不是会背了吗？\NHamnet, I thought you'd already learnt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.28,0:46:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了 因为把课本落学堂了\NI didn't because I left my primer at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.95,0:46:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 哈姆奈特\NWell, Hamnet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.45,0:46:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你要用心学\Nyou need to take your studies seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.77,0:46:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不努力怎么会进步...\NHow do you expect to improve if you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.15,0:46:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,（希腊语）吾不肯苟且而生 不甘平庸而逝
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.15,0:46:53.57,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读荷马《伊利亚特》第22卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.57,0:46:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,（希腊语）愿成就丰功伟绩 令后世永传吾名
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.57,0:46:58.61,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《伊利亚特》: 荷马(古希腊诗人)史诗 论英雄 战争与命运】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.38,0:47:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群小淘气\NYou rascals.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.82,0:47:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们耍到你了吗？ - 当然了\N- Did we trick you? - Of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.55,0:47:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们又互换来耍我\NYou swapped places to hoodwink me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.12,0:47:09.79,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 当时女性普遍无法接受正规教育 现实中他妻女都不识字】
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.80,0:47:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 过来\NSusanna, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.14,0:47:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.25,0:47:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还记得要给你娘准备的那件事吗？\NNow, do you remember the thing we were going to do for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.10,0:47:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 都记得吗？准备好了吗？\N- Yeah. - You remember? You ready to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.61,0:47:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 好 快去 快去准备\N- Yeah. - Okay. Go outside quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.39,0:47:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快去 快去 快去\NGo, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.99,0:47:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 朝前走 - 别急\N- Just step toward... - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.64,0:47:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再走 往右走 小心\NOne st-- Come to your right. Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.96,0:47:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点 再迈一步\NStep. One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.29,0:47:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啥 - 再迈一步\N- What. - One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们三个儿啥时候再聚？\NWhen shall we three meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.39,0:47:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等打雷 等闪电 还是等下雨？\NIn thunder, lightning or in rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.60,0:47:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等到这场吵闹都停了 等到这一仗打出个输赢了\NWhen hurly-burly's done, when the battle's lost and won!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.96,0:47:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那就在太阳落山以前\NThat will be ere at set of sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.65,0:47:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在什么地方？ - 就在荒原\N- Where the place? - Upon the heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.32,0:48:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿同安妮丝会面\NThere to meet with Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.33,0:48:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 灰妖猫\NI come, Graymalkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.92,0:48:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤蟆叫\NPaddock calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.84,0:48:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,马上到\NAnon!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.58,0:48:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,美即是丑 丑即是美\NFair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.50,0:48:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,美即是丑 丑即是美 美即是丑 丑即是美\NFair is foul and foul is fair. Fair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.87,0:48:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,美即是丑 丑即是美\NFair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.87,0:48:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,穿入到...\NHover through the...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.88,0:48:18.36,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《麦克白》: 出自第一幕第一场 参考卞之琳译本】
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.37,0:48:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,演得好\NWell done!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.45,0:48:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真精彩\NThat was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.80,0:48:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,挖深点 把土拨到一边\NDig it deep, and then you move all of it to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.33,0:48:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把根放进去\Nand then you put it down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.28,0:48:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吧？然后把土填回去\NRight? And then you get the soil around the sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.41,0:48:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,用手把土拍平\Nand then you pat it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.24,0:48:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后手上就沾了土\NAnd then you get bits like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.49,0:48:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两手搓一搓\NAnd you rub it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.87,0:48:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 向后退\NWhoa. And then back!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.38,0:48:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,照我这样做\NDo this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.77,0:48:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后转圈 盯住对手\NAnd when you're doing this, circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.28,0:48:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是这样\NYeah, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.12,0:48:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,前进 后撤\NForward. And back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.73,0:48:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 挡剑 挡剑 挡剑\NNow, parry, parry, parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.95,0:48:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 再来\NGood. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.43,0:49:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接着 我出这招\NNow, after that one, I'm gonna do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.83,0:49:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要闪开\Nand you get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.09,0:49:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？绕圈走 转动你的剑\NReady? Circle off. Spin your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.29,0:49:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.61,0:49:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,绕圈 把剑转起来\NCircle, spin your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.20,0:49:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 向前迈\NNow, come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.70,0:49:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再往后退\NAnd go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,挡剑三次\NOne, two three.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.03,0:49:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开\NOut of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.27,0:49:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 再来一次\NVery good. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.57,0:49:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝 闻闻这是什么？\NJudith, what's this one called?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.21,0:49:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 百里香 百里香 - 是迷迭香\N- Thyme. Thyme. - Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.46,0:49:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是百里香 - 好吧 百里香 百里香\N-Thyme. - Thyme. Thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.22,0:49:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我记错了 - 没关系\N- I got it mixed up. - That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.28,0:49:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这株是...\NThis one...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.75,0:49:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是迷迭香 - 对\N- Now, that's rosemary. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.07,0:49:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,迷迭香有什么用处？\NAnd what is rosemary for?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.84,0:49:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放在苹果里一起炖 - 炖苹果\N- Putting it in apples. - Apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.89,0:49:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 再闻闻\NNo. What is Rosemary's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.52,0:49:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 记忆 - 纪念\N- Remembering. - Remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.78,0:49:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对 记忆纪念\NRemembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.44,0:49:44.52,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 这些草药名字也出现在威廉现实著作中】
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.09,0:50:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 搓一搓\NNow, you're to rub all this in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.77,0:50:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吹个小心愿进去\NYou blow a little wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.32,0:50:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,许个愿 让他带走\NTo wish him on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.74,0:50:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？这就是你和他的小秘密了\NYeah? And it's your secret with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.97,0:50:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗？\NDid you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.35,0:50:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没看见在天上吗？\NDid you not see him in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.06,0:50:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再来一次\NAll right, do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.20,0:50:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再许个愿\NMake another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.75,0:50:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看 就在上面\NLook. Right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.26,0:50:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那里 看见了吗？\NLook, just there. Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.88,0:51:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他把你们所有的愿望都藏在他的小心窝里\NAnd he's got all your wishes tucked in his little heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.24,0:51:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,每当想念他的时候\NSo any time that you want to remember him,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.76,0:51:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要抬头去...\Nyou just have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.33,0:51:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.83,0:51:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你\NHuh? I'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.99,0:51:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你\NI'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.47,0:51:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爹？\NFather?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.59,0:51:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？\NIs all well?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.41,0:51:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.84,0:51:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 别太靠近你爷爷\NListen, I want you to stay away from your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.06,0:51:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会打你姐妹 但我担心你 \NHe'll not hit your sisters, but it's you that I worry for,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.57,0:51:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当我走了你要能保护好自己\Nand I need to know that you'll be safe when I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.22,0:51:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,又要回伦敦了么？\NYou're going back to London again?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.34,0:51:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对 明天\NYes, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.74,0:51:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就走？\NTomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.37,0:51:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.29,0:51:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们能跟你一起去吗？\NWill we go with you this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.18,0:51:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 还不行\NNo, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.68,0:52:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.38,0:52:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想念你的\NI'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.02,0:52:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我得走 你明白吗？我得...\NBut I have to go, you understand? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.40,0:52:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.40,0:52:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.74,0:52:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.46,0:52:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要替我照顾好你娘和你姐妹\N'Cause I need you to look after your mother and your sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.85,0:52:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能做到吗？\NWill you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.29,0:52:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,能\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.71,0:52:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能做个男子汉吗？ - 能\N- Will you be brave? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.29,0:52:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.16,0:52:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你勇敢吗？ - 是\N- Will you be brave? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.18,0:52:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是男子汉吗？\NWill you be brave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.00,0:52:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？ - 是 是 我是男子汉\N- Huh?! - Yes! Yes, I'll be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.12,0:52:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢 我是男子汉\NI'll be brave. I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.97,0:52:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在伦敦替咱们物色好房子了\NI've looked at houses for us in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.14,0:52:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 秋天就要来了 - 嗯\N-Autumn is coming. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.51,0:52:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们会生病的\NAnd the children will fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.97,0:52:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝还是太虚弱了\NJudith, she's still not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.00,0:52:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她常常胸闷\NShe often gets congestion in her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.60,0:53:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦那空气...\NAnd the air in London is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.12,0:53:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去不了\NWe can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.95,0:53:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但迟早有一天 我们会去的\NBut one day soon, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.73,0:53:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会跟你去伦敦的\NWe will come to London with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.27,0:53:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的\NNo, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.03,0:53:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会来的\NYou'll never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.94,0:53:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天你嫌太热\NYou've waited for the heat of summer to pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.29,0:53:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,秋天干燥\N...the dryness of autumn,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.56,0:53:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天太冷\Nthe snow and the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.10,0:53:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你压根儿不信珠迪丝能在伦敦活着\NYou do not believe that Judith will ever survive London.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.90,0:53:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你会想尽一切办法保住那孩子\NYou'd do anything in your power to keep that child alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.37,0:53:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,做母亲不就该这样吗？\NIsn't that what a mother is supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.36,0:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是\NOf course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.53,0:53:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.28,0:53:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定就在这镇子附近给咱们找个家\N...I've decided to look for land outside Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.25,0:53:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你和孩子们还在斯特拉特福镇这片生活\NThat's where you should live with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.25,0:53:55.90,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【斯特拉特福: 距离伦敦160公里 当时为羊毛 皮革等畜产品加工地】
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.90,0:53:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你 - 嗯\N- Thank you. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.02,0:54:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.08,0:54:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来 啊\NWhere is she? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.63,0:54:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特呢 你来了\NHamnet. There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.54,0:54:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.45,0:54:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你 爱你 爱你\NI love you. I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.29,0:54:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 来亲一下\NAll right. Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.63,0:54:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 - 来亲一下\N- Come on. - Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.08,0:54:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来亲一下\NLove you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.04,0:54:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.97,0:54:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 过来\NAll right. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.15,0:54:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还记得我告诉你的话吗？ - 记得\N- Remember what I told you, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.63,0:54:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\NGood boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.13,0:54:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要走了 - 再见\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.36,0:54:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走了 - 走吧\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.23,0:55:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真走了 - 走吧\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.80,0:55:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 哈姆奈特？\NHamnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.15,0:55:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 到这儿来\NCome on. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.66,0:55:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把手给我\NShow me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.63,0:55:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你看到什么了？\NWhat? What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.22,0:55:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你...\NI see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.03,0:55:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,长大了\NGrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.30,0:55:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,身强力壮\NAnd very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.92,0:55:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我还看到你在伦敦 和你父亲一起工作\NAnd I see you in London working with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.46,0:56:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在剧院吗？ - 对\N- In the theater? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.52,0:56:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在剧场\NAt the playhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.99,0:56:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在那儿做什么？\NWhat will I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.73,0:56:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么呢？\NWhat do you wish to do, Hamnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.77,0:56:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想当个拿剑的演员\NI should be one of the players with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.80,0:56:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拿剑的？\NA sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.42,0:56:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.71,0:56:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想拿剑和其他演员交锋\NAnd I shall clash it against the sword of the other player.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.50,0:56:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,示范给我看看\NShow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.03,0:56:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,会有场激烈的战斗\NThere'll be a terrible fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.77,0:56:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,观众看得心惊胆战\Nand everybody watching will be frightened out of their wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.68,0:56:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那谁会赢呢？\NAnd who will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.48,0:56:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自然是我\NI shall, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.04,0:56:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是你\NOf course you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.81,0:56:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被什么惊到了\NSomething has upset them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.05,0:56:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.31,0:56:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是天气\NThe weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.98,0:56:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,或者空气里有什么 不确定\NSomething in the air, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.91,0:57:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉琼今天别让孩子们出门了\NBest tell Joan to keep the children inside today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.76,0:59:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝？\NJudith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.14,1:00:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝？\NJudith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.11,1:00:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿呢？\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.81,1:00:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒啊\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.15,1:00:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,面包师的猫生小猫咪了\NThe baker told me her cat had kittens.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.91,1:00:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们得去看看\NWe need to see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.42,1:00:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有八只呢 珠迪丝 八只\NThere's eight, Judith. Eight!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.55,1:00:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得抓紧了 要下雨了\NWe need to hurry. It's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.60,1:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝？\NJudith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.57,1:00:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小珠？\NJude?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.25,1:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.79,1:00:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿不舒服？珠迪丝\NWhat's wrong, Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.39,1:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你说话啊 珠迪丝\NJudith, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.62,1:00:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,起来啊\NJudith, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.60,1:00:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 珠迪丝 说句话\NJudith, please. Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.06,1:01:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？ - 是珠迪丝\N- What is it? - It's Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.15,1:01:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她这样多久了？\NHow long has she been like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.46,1:01:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我从学堂回来她就这样了\NSince I returned from school.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.54,1:01:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.70,1:01:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她得上了\NShe's got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.55,1:01:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是？\NHasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.23,1:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她得了瘟疫\NShe's got the pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.89,1:01:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 娘？\NHasn't she, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.67,1:01:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去找你奶奶\NGo find your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.06,1:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让她马上来\NBid her to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.54,1:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快去\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.56,1:01:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她烧得厉害\NShe's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.61,1:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,得要水 要很多水\NWe need, um, more water.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.03,1:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,烧大火 把水烧热了\NMake a bigger fire and heat up more water.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.79,1:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要热水 - 伊莱莎 去打些水来\N- We need warm water. - Eliza, fetch more water
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.02,1:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把厨房的白雏菊也拿来\Nand bring the Bellis from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.22,1:01:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再拿肉桂\NA row of cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.74,1:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,肉桂能退烧\NCinnamon, that's good for drawing out the heat.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.94,1:01:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还要松草或者芸香 百里香也要\NPineweed or a rue. Thyme, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.58,1:01:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去屋里找\NYou'll find them in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.13,1:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘啊 - 屋里那张桌子边 桌子边\N- Mama. Yeah. - The other table. The other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.55,1:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿呢 我的心肝\NYeah, Mama's here, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.94,1:02:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来 喝这个 迷迭香熬的药膏\NHere, drink this. It's rosemary and jelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.38,1:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,会没事吗？\NAll will be well, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.98,1:02:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都会没事的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.30,1:02:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝 坚持住\NJudith, stay with.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.38,1:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿 没事的 娘在这儿\NMama's here. It's okay. Mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.42,1:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大黄 咱们得要大黄 能清肠子\NRhubarb. We need rhubarb to purge the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.20,1:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱瘟疫\Ndrive out the pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.21,1:02:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去取吗？\NCan you go and fetch some?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.53,1:02:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿 没事的 珠迪丝 大家都在\NMama's here. It's okay. Judith, we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.78,1:02:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 你也去打些水来\NSusanna, draw some water, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.30,1:02:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特和玛丽还有苏珊娜\NHamnet and... and Mary and Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.09,1:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快去打水\NDraw water as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.81,1:02:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么还没来呢？\NWhy isn't he here?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.66,1:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱莎 去给你哥哥威廉写信 让他赶快回来\NEliza, go write to your brother and tell him to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.78,1:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝\NJudith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.31,1:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 珠迪丝\NOpen your mouth, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.57,1:02:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 娘在这儿 对 很好\NOpen your mouth. Mama's here. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.65,1:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.31,1:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对 会没事的\NYes, you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.35,1:02:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 都喝下去\NYou'll open your mouth. Drink it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.76,1:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下去 娘在这儿 别怕 珠迪丝\NSwallow it down. Mama's here. It's okay, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.33,1:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿 别怕\NMama's here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.60,1:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.63,1:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.99,1:03:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.97,1:03:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\NYou have done all that you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.32,1:03:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会放手的\NI will not let her cross over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.82,1:03:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 你失去的三个女儿...\NGrandmama, you had three daughters that were taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.97,1:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也是像...\NWere they...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.55,1:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也是像珠迪丝这样吗？\NWere they like Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.36,1:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮那时七岁\NAnne was seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.39,1:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,另两个还只是吃奶的婴儿\NThe other two were just babies.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.06,1:04:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都长了肿块...\NThey all had swellings and...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.06,1:04:14.43,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【腺鼠疫: 会导致淋巴结肿大 常见于颈部 腋下和腹股沟】
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.44,1:04:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都发高烧 跟珠迪丝一样\N...fever like Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.94,1:04:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你娘在...\NYour mother's trying to...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.52,1:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命想保住她的孩子\Nkeep a grip on her child.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.50,1:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的\NIt won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.62,1:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,命是天给的 随时都能被收回\NWhat is given may be taken away at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.90,1:04:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得时刻提防着\NWe must never let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.72,1:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别把孩子们的...\NNever take for granted...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.83,1:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次心跳...\N...that our children's hearts beat,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.31,1:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次呼吸...\Nthat they draw breath,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.95,1:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的行走 说话...\Nthat they walk and speak and...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.29,1:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,欢笑 吵闹和嬉戏当作理所当然的\N...smile, argue, play.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.36,1:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,得时刻提醒自己 他们可能说没就没了\NNever forget for a moment that they may be gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.42,1:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹\NJude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.68,1:05:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小珠\NJude.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.60,1:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别难过\NDon't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.74,1:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要替我好好活下去\NYou shall be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.80,1:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\NI shall not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.19,1:06:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我活不下去\NNot without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.52,1:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它来了\NIt's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.14,1:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹 你看得到吗？\NDo you see it, Jude?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.43,1:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它在看着咱们呢\NIt's watching us.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.75,1:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉它把咱们都带走\NI'll tell it to take us both.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.11,1:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要走一起走\NWe'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.69,1:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去\NTurn away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.08,1:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去\NTurn away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.22,1:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它会看错的\NIt'll make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.42,1:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它分不出咱们俩谁是谁\NIt can't tell us apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.04,1:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起呼吸 珠迪丝\NBreathe with me, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.20,1:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的命给你\NI give you my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.19,1:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的\NYou shall be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.55,1:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的命换你 珠迪丝\NI give you my life, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.68,1:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.33,1:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男子汉 爹\NI'll be brave, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.81,1:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.30,1:08:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.74,1:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男子汉 爹\NI'll be brave, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.49,1:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男子汉\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.66,1:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.63,1:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,驭\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.76,1:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快\NQuick as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.16,1:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特\NHamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.83,1:09:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 你不该在这儿睡\NHamnet, you're not supposed to be down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.20,1:09:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来 我抱你上楼睡觉去...\NI need to take you up to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.13,1:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特\NHamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？\NHamnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.91,1:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.69,1:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.38,1:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,娘啊\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.69,1:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特\NHamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.68,1:11:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你得张开嘴\NYou must open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.83,1:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,会没事的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.85,1:11:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他在发烧\NHe's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.59,1:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,烧得太高了\NHe's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.01,1:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,药不起作用 不起作用\NIt will not sti-- It will not stick!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.20,1:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拿石头 拿石头\NA stone. There's a stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.20,1:11:50.35,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【有洞的石头: 当时民间信仰认为病气能从一孔进 一孔出】
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.51,1:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,楼上有块中间有洞的石头\NThere's a stone upstairs with a hole in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.32,1:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在他床边 快去拿来 快去\NBy his bedside. Bring it down. I need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.35,1:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还要盐 拿盐 得撒盐\NAnd, um, uh, salt. Get salt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.35,1:11:56.69,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【撒盐: 当时认为能建立保护屏障 驱挡邪灵和病气】
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.51,1:11:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能去拿吗？\NGet it. Can you give it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.80,1:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,多拿点盐 有多少拿多少\NCan you f-fetch me some salt, as much salt as you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.69,1:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,水 还要水\NWater. We need water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.37,1:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他烧得太厉害了\NHe's... he's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.31,1:12:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了\NHe's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.84,1:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子 娘在这儿\NMy love. Mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.90,1:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 都会好的\NAll will be well. All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.85,1:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都会好的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.86,1:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,都会好的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.23,1:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 别怕\NHamnet, don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.54,1:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的\NNo need to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.15,1:12:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都会没事的 娘在这儿\NAll will be well. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.13,1:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在 没事的\NMommy's here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.81,1:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿\NMommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.22,1:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 娘在这儿\NLook at me. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.01,1:12:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不 绝不会放手的\NI will never, ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.30,1:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.19,1:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,娘绝不 绝不会放手的\NI will never, ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.99,1:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,娘的心肝啊\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.51,1:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,心肝啊\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.40,1:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱莎 把珠迪丝抱到厨房去\NEliza, take Judith to the kitchen and keep her there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.61,1:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.94,1:12:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我得陪他 - 带她走\N- He needs me! - Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.24,1:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要陪我哥\NHe needs me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.63,1:13:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.37,1:13:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,缬草啊...\NValerian...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.60,1:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 哈姆奈特 哈姆奈特\NHamnet. Hamnet. Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.39,1:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 坚持住 求你了\NHamnet, you have to stay. Hamnet, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.29,1:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 你要坚持住 别离开我们\NHamnet, please. You have to stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.30,1:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,娘需要你 我们都需要你\NMama needs you. We need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.90,1:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住手 够了 - 别离开我们 坚持住 坚持\N- Stop! Enough! - Stay with us. Stay, stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.10,1:13:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了 哈姆奈特 坚持住 坚持住\NPlease, Hamnet. Hamnet, Hamnet, Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.53,1:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别折腾他了 - 求求你了 哈姆奈特\N- Let him alone! - Hamnet, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.89,1:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不出来吗 太晚了\NCan't you see that it's too late for him!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.04,1:13:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了\NPlease, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.39,1:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特？\NHamnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.82,1:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 哈姆奈特 求你了 哈姆奈特\NHamnet. Hamnet. Please. Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.35,1:14:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子没了\NMy son is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.77,1:14:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没了 我的儿子\NJust so bereft... it's my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.43,1:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没了 我...\NI've lost my...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.82,1:15:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我看灯还亮着 我也睡不着\NI saw the light, and I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.49,1:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.14,1:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 孩子 不行\NOh, child, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.72,1:16:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 快去睡觉 - 没事 没事 让她看吧\N- No, no, no. Go to bed. - No, no, let-let her stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.08,1:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是我害的 娘 都是我害的\NIt is my fault, Mama. It is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.28,1:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\NNo. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.20,1:16:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝 这不是你的错\NIt is not your fault, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.16,1:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他替了我\NBut he changed places with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.35,1:16:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了它\NHe tricked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.75,1:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了什么？\NHe tricked what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.21,1:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,死神\NDeath.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.83,1:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝\NJudith.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.94,1:16:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它来找我时 却把他夺走了\NIt took him when it came for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.44,1:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这话绝对不许再说\NNever say those words to anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.93,1:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥是因为发烧走的\NThe fever came for your brother, and it took him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.88,1:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看看他吗？\NDo you wish to see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.38,1:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.39,1:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 去看看他\NGo on. You can see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.27,1:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是他吗？\NIs it really him?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.77,1:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.79,1:17:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这 这不像我哥\NIt-it doesn't look like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.59,1:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.59,1:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是他\NIt's not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.25,1:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NIt's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.06,1:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我哥\NIt's not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.78,1:17:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天还没亮呢\NIt-It's-it's not morning yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.51,1:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还没给他收拾好呢\NWe haven't prepared him properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.19,1:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我来晚了吗？\NAm I too late?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.30,1:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是你 - 爹\N- It's you. - Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.45,1:17:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是你\NIt's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.70,1:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是我\NIt's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.01,1:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子呢？\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.52,1:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿...\NWhere is...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.53,1:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他在...\NWhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.84,1:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是我儿子\NIt's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.43,1:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的儿子啊\NIt's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.18,1:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我没预见到\NI didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.19,1:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我该多留心哈姆奈特的\NI should've paid him more attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.52,1:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为会失去珠迪丝\NI always thought she was the one to be taken away
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.64,1:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到是儿子\Nwhen all the while it was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.06,1:20:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我太蠢了\NI'm a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.07,1:20:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 没人能救他\NNo, there's nothing anyone could have done to save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.96,1:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\NYou did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.70,1:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尽力了\NOf course I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.17,1:20:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可你人呢？\NYou weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.81,1:20:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿把心掏给他\NI would have cut my heart out and given it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.60,1:20:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的命换他的命\NI would have laid my life down on the ground for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.45,1:20:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我懂 我懂 - 可上天不收\N- I-I know. I know. - And no one would take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.36,1:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可你... - 不 你不懂\N- But you... - No, you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.13,1:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能懂 你都不在啊\NYou don't know. You weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.56,1:20:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他在折磨中死去\NHe died in agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.22,1:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.59,1:20:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 受尽了折磨 - 安妮丝\N- He was in agony. - Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.53,1:20:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他哭个不停 他哭啊 哭啊\NHe cried and he cried
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.07,1:20:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-  哭啊 哭啊 哭啊 - 安妮丝 别这样\N- and he cried and he cried. - Agnes, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.75,1:20:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他小小的身子在剧痛中抽搐 - 嘘\N- And his little body was wracked in pain. - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.34,1:20:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别让我闭嘴\NNo, don't shush me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.60,1:20:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时好害怕\NHe was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.00,1:20:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你却没在身边 - 我知道\N- And you weren't here. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.99,1:20:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么办法都用了\NI tried everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.82,1:20:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做了\NI know you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.55,1:21:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我什么都试过了 - 你已经尽了一切\N- I tried everything I could. - You did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.26,1:21:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经用尽了一切办法\NYou did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.00,1:21:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一切办法\NEverything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.12,1:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一切办法\NEverything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.60,1:21:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝\NAgnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.48,1:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我会捎信的 安妮丝\NI will send word, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.46,1:21:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,捎信？\NYou'll send word?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.02,1:21:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 捎给谁啊？ - 给你啊\N- To whom? - To you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.86,1:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿啊\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.98,1:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说到了伦敦我会给你捎信的\NWhat I meant was that I shall send word when I reach London.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.55,1:22:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦？\NLondon?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.71,1:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\NI must leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.81,1:22:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,走？你怎么能走？\NLeave? How can you leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.60,1:22:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,世界不会因为我们就停下来 安妮丝\NThe world does simply not stand still, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.02,1:22:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦还有人在等我\NThere are people waiting for me in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.41,1:22:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,演出季马上就要开始了\NThe season is about to begin,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.77,1:22:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的剧团随时都会从肯特郡回来\Nand my company shall return from Kent any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.56,1:22:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就得走了\NI have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.12,1:22:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在？\NNow?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.31,1:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有个商队要出发\NThere's a traveling party leaving today,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.01,1:22:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有匹多余的马 现在就得走\Nand they have a spare horse, so yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.64,1:22:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,照看好女儿们 我回来时会...\NLook after the girls, and I will return to--
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.64,1:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.77,1:22:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.54,1:23:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 你走吧\NGo. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.34,1:23:34.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(995,655)\frz7.1\fax-0.15\an8\fnSource Han Serif SC\b1\c&H0F0F0F&\fs90}哈姆奈特
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.84,1:23:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“蒙晨暮鼓催岁长”\N"When I do count the clock that tells the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.51,1:23:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“夕太沉沉入幽光”\N"And see the brave day sunk in hideous night;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.39,1:23:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“芳草奇花香自散”\N"When I behold the violet past prime,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.87,1:23:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“青丝墨字今已霜”\N"And sable curls all silver'd o'er with white;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.94,1:23:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,“繁荫不复幕沧桑”\N"When lofty trees I see barren of leaves
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.03,1:23:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“牧群归舍众组忙”\N"Which erst from the heat did canopy the herd,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.84,1:23:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,“夏末青禾束成囊”\N"And summer's green all girded up in sheaves
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.97,1:23:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,“犹似亡魂缠白裳”\N"Borne on the bier with white and bristly beard;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.86,1:24:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“容颜岂非浮云妆”\N"Then of thy beauty do I question make,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.36,1:24:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“终将消散入苍茫”\N"Thou among the wastes of time must go,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.34,1:24:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“芬芳娇艳随风扬”\N"Since sweets and beauties do themselves forsake
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.15,1:24:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,“新生如笋催人苍”\N"And die as fast as they see others grow;
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.43,1:24:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“时光镰刀谁能挡”\N"And nothing gainst time's scythe can make defense
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.54,1:24:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“勇敢生育续春阳”\NSave breed, to brave him when he takes thee hence."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.54,1:24:20.97,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【十四行诗: 现代编号第12首 以时间流逝与生育为主题】
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.97,1:24:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能再读一遍吗？\NWill you read it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.32,1:24:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不了\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.95,1:24:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经读了三遍了\NI've read it three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.01,1:24:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\NThat's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.01,1:24:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们开始拆礼物吧 - 什么礼物？伦敦的吗？\N- Shall we do presents? - Presents? from London?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.62,1:24:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给你的梳子 小珠\NA hair comb for you, Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.84,1:24:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爱惜点用 别弄坏了\NMind you, you'll have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.28,1:24:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给你的 安妮丝\NThis is for you, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.36,1:25:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 红宝石吗？ - 是的\N- A ruby, is it? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.03,1:25:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过这么漂亮的\NIt's the finest I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.28,1:25:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在议论那栋新房子\NEveryone's talking about the new house.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.83,1:25:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是斯特拉特福镇上最大的房子\NIt's the biggest in Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.68,1:25:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,房间多到人进去都能走丢\NThere are so many rooms. One could get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.57,1:25:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 那就好好照看好\NYou shall keep the keys, Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.95,1:25:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,打理好咱们的房子\NYou shall manage the house well.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.86,1:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘 你戴上试试\NPut it on, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.41,1:25:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥巴塞洛缪带你看过那栋房子了吗？\NDid Bartholomew show you the new house?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.71,1:25:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看了\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.27,1:25:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗？\NDo you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.53,1:25:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不亲自带我去看的？\NWhy didn't you show me yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.38,1:25:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是怕我不愿离开吗？\NWere you afraid I wouldn't leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.65,1:26:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为哈姆奈特死在这个房子里\N'Cause Hamnet died here in this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.13,1:26:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想他在哪儿？\NYou know, I'm constantly wondering where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.38,1:26:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他去了哪儿？\NOr where he has gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.02,1:26:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我做什么 脑子里都是他在哪儿？\NWhatever I'm doing, I'm wondering, "Where is he?"
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.73,1:26:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能就这么凭空没了啊\NI mean, he can't have just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.76,1:26:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要找到他\NAll he needs is for me to find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.78,1:26:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定在哪个地方\NHe must be somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.36,1:26:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都一年了还是这样 我真害怕自己会疯掉\NI fear I may run mad with it, even now, a year on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.35,1:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一年算什么啊\NA year is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.46,1:26:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一年什么都不是 每时每刻...\NA year is nothing. It's every second...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.42,1:26:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,每分每秒 每天每年\Nevery minute, every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.04,1:26:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能停止寻找啊\NWe may never stop looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.77,1:26:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 安妮丝\NI'm sorry, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.80,1:27:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗？我说对不起 安妮丝\NDid you hear me? I said that I'm sorry, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.21,1:27:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么道歉？ - 为这一切\N- For what? - For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.50,1:27:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你被那地方缠住了 - 为...\N- You're caught by that place. - For...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.02,1:27:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么地方？ - 你脑子里那个地方\N- What place? - That place in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.95,1:27:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说 那地方比什么都好\NIt is now more real to you than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.62,1:27:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,连咱儿子死了都留不住你\NNot even the death of our child can keep you from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.97,1:27:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特死了\NHamnet died.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.29,1:27:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,死得很惨\NA horrible death.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.46,1:27:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你本该在场\NAnd you should have been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.78,1:27:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可跟他道个别\NYou could have bid him farewell.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.67,1:27:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么？\NWhat do you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.05,1:28:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.95,1:28:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.22,1:28:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有？\NNothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.98,1:28:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\NNothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.95,1:28:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOh, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.38,1:28:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是回伦敦吧\NYou should go back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.74,1:28:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不用为我们操心\NYou need not concern yourself with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.37,1:28:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我们的日子也照过\NGet along just fine without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.19,1:28:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“这句话从前是个似是而非的悖论”\NThis was sometime a paradox,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.38,1:28:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“如今已被时间所证实”\Nbut now the time gives it proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.67,1:28:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“我确实曾爱过你”\NI did love you once.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.50,1:28:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“没错 殿下 您确实让我信以为真”\NIndeed, my lord, you made me believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.34,1:28:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“你当初就不该相信我”\NYou should not have believed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.69,1:28:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“美德嫁接到我们这罪恶的老树干上 也...”\Nfor virtue cannot so inoculate our old stock for...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.15,1:29:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,“你当初就不该相信我”\NYou should not have believed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.04,1:29:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,“美德嫁接到我们这罪恶的老树干上”\Nfor virtue cannot so inoculate our old stock
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.89,1:29:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“也结不出好果”\Nbut we shall relish of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.77,1:29:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“我从未真爱过你”\NI loved you not.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.66,1:29:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“那我真是被深深欺骗了”\NI was the more deceived.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.38,1:29:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“去美人庵吧”\NGet thee to a nunnery.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.38,1:29:21.22,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【美人庵: 指女性宗教修行场所 又为妓院俚语 此处含贬低之意】
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.99,1:29:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“干嘛非得生出一堆罪人来？”\NWhy wouldst thou be a breeder of sinners?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.22,1:29:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.65,1:29:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清”\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.79,1:29:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“最大的莫过于...”\Nthat it were better to...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.79,1:29:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,重来\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.36,1:29:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“去美人庵吧”\NGet thee to a nunnery.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.45,1:29:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“干嘛非得生出一堆罪人来？”\NWhy wouldst thou be a breeder of sinners?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.31,1:29:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己也算个老实人 但...”\NI am myself indifferent honest, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.73,1:29:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,重来 是“我自己还算个老实人” 重来\NAgain. "I am myself indifferent honest." Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.77,1:29:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.80,1:29:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清 最大的莫过于”\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things that it were better
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.26,1:29:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我娘把我生了出来” - 重来\N- my mother had not borne me. - Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.98,1:29:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“我这个人...”\NI, myself...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.63,1:29:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃... - 再来\N- And... - Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.53,1:29:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“我这个人...自己还算个...”\NI, myself, am indifferent...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.21,1:29:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是“我自己”\N"I am myself."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.85,1:29:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.93,1:30:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清...”\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things that it were...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.10,1:30:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再来\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.43,1:30:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清...”\NBut yet I could accuse me of such things that it were...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.05,1:30:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再来\NAgain!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.47,1:30:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.07,1:30:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过...”\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.06,1:30:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没投入\NYou are simply mouthing the words!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.51,1:30:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己还算个老实人\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.78,1:30:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的罪过却多得数不清\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.07,1:30:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的莫过于我娘把我生了出来\Nthat it were better my mother had not borne me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.65,1:30:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人自傲 报复心强 野心大\NI am very proud, revengeful, ambitious,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.82,1:30:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子里装的那些坏主意\Nwith more offenses at my beck
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.52,1:30:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多到我都数不清\Nthan I have thoughts to put them in,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.23,1:30:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想都想不尽 干也干不完\Nimagination to give them shape or time to act them in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.33,1:30:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这样的人\NNow, what should such fellows as I do
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.02,1:30:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在天地之间苟活 有什么用？\Ncrawling between heaven and earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.85,1:30:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们全是烂透的坏人\NWe are arrant knaves all.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.24,1:30:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你可千万不要信我们\NBelieve none of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.96,1:30:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的美人庵吧 重来\NGo thy ways to a nunnery. Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.67,1:31:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,生存...\NTo be...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.26,1:31:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还是毁灭...\N...or not to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.91,1:31:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个问题\N...that is the question:
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.58,1:32:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种更高贵？是默然 忍受...\NWhether 'tis nobler in the mind to... suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.30,1:32:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,命运投来的巨石...\NThe slings and arrows of...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.73,1:32:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,射来的毒箭？\N...outrageous fortune...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.25,1:32:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还是...\N...Or...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.04,1:32:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,挺身反抗...\N...to take arms against a...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.76,1:32:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,无涯的苦海...\N...sea of troubles,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.10,1:32:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,通过斗争...\NAnd by opposing...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.30,1:32:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,渡向彼岸？\N...end them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.95,1:33:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈求那些树啊 ♪\N♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.17,1:33:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 还我男孩来 ♪\N♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.34,1:33:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 只因... ♪\N♪ For ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.59,1:33:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 那只温柔的知更鸟 ♪\N♪ Sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.85,1:33:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 是我仅有的幸福 ♪\N♪ Is all my joy. ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.85,1:33:52.76,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《我那去了绿林的知更鸟》: 英国民谣 绿林象征来世 知更鸟象征逝者】
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.28,1:33:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝？\NAgnes?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.68,1:34:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我碰巧来镇上\NI... I was in town, and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.77,1:34:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就想顺路来看下你\NI thought I would pay you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.38,1:34:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你公公约翰去世了 替你们难过\NI was very sorry to hear about John's passing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.46,1:34:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫还好吧\NHow's your husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.23,1:34:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,失去父亲 真是件悲痛的事啊\NIt's a... it's a terrible thing to lose one's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.24,1:34:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他好得很\NHe's well.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.83,1:34:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,忙得要命 还在搞一出喜剧\NHe's very busy. He's preparing a comedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.58,1:34:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他的新剧可不是喜剧\NHis new play is not a comedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.35,1:34:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是悲剧\NIt's a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.52,1:34:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该早知道了\NBut you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.02,1:34:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,镇上人人都在谈论\NEveryone in town is talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.88,1:34:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是劝过你别嫁给他...\NI did warn you about marrying him...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.13,1:34:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别装作疼我\NDon't pretend that you care for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.23,1:34:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我娘 永远也不会是\NYou are not my mother, and you never were.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.94,1:35:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 安妮丝\NGood day, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.00,1:35:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他都好几个月没跟我们联系了\NHe's not spoken to us for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.41,1:35:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么能\NHow could he...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.79,1:35:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么能不告诉我们呢？\NHow could he not tell us?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.65,1:35:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想看看吗？\NDo you not wonder what is in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.43,1:35:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么？\NIn what?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.31,1:35:20.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\frz-33.0\fax-0.05\an8\fnSource Han Serif SC\b1\c&H0F0F0F&\fs90\move(1164,733,1101,620,1460,2300)}《哈姆雷特的悲剧》
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.71,1:35:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这剧\NThe play.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.10,1:36:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们找谁呢？\NWho are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.48,1:36:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·莎士比亚\NWilliam Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.98,1:36:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是他的家人 从斯特拉特福来的\NWe're his family from Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.86,1:36:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上楼 他住阁楼\NGo up the stairs. He lives in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.14,1:37:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有斯特拉特福最大房子的人\NWhy would the man with the largest house in Stratford
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.46,1:37:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会住在这样的地方？\Nbe living here?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.97,1:37:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.37,1:37:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为...\NI thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.34,1:37:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他...\NI thought he...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.70,1:37:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？\NWhat shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.79,1:37:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,敞开心扉\NKeep your heart open.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.60,1:37:48.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,276)\frx48.0\frz0.5\fay0.04\an8\b1\fs90\1c&H6F7480&\3c&&H2F2D66&\bord6\shad0\alpha&HFF&\t(0,550,\alpha&H00&)}天下皆为舞{\alpha&HFF&\t(500,2700,{\alpha&H00&}台
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.60,1:37:48.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【拉丁格言"天下皆为舞台 人人都是演员" 莎士比亚《皆大欢喜》亦用此意象】
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.66,1:37:56.33,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965,512)\an8\b1\fs12\1c&H4B525C\3c&&H2F2D66&\bord0.1\shad0\fscx95\fscy95\t(0,7666,\fscx100\fscy100)}天下皆为舞台
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.33,1:38:00.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\move(974,274,974,244,0,3959)\frx-50.0\an8\b1\fs50\1c&H4B525C\3c&&H2F2D66&\bord1\shad0\fscx95\fscy95\t(0,1,\fscx100\fscy100)}天下皆为舞台
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.59,1:38:26.78,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 当时剧场分为站票 看台 包厢等级】
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.80,1:39:10.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（《哈姆奈特的悲剧》）
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.10,1:39:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁呀？ - 不 先回答我\N- Who's there? - Nay, answer me:
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.76,1:39:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 报上名来\Nstand and unfold yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.88,1:39:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,国王万岁\NLong live the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.88,1:39:39.42,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【国王万岁: 执勤人员碰头暗号】
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.43,1:39:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,伯纳多？\NBernardo?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.42,1:39:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是碰到我的夜班同伴\NIf you do meet Horatio and Marcellus,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.60,1:39:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,霍拉旭和马塞拉斯 叫他们速来\NThe rivals to my watch, bid them make haste.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.88,1:39:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们好像来了 站住 谁\NI think I hear them. Stand, ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.75,1:39:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？\NWho's there?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.66,1:39:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它今晚又现身了吗？\NHas this thing appeared again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.89,1:39:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没看见 - 霍拉旭说...\N- I have seen nothing. - Horatio says...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.72,1:39:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这演的什么啊\NWhat are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.72,1:39:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这不过是我们的幻觉\N...'tis but our fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.45,1:40:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾和他说过 他就是不信...\N...and will not let belief take hold of him touching...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.95,1:40:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我儿子有什么关系？\NWhat has any of this to do with my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.95,1:40:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们已经见过两次这可怕的景象...\N...this dreaded sight twice seen of us...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.99,1:40:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很害怕\NThese men are frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.65,1:40:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好怕的\NOf what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.54,1:40:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}别不信 让我们再给你解释一遍...\NAnd let us once again assail your ears...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.92,1:40:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在提防一个幽灵\NThey watch for a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.07,1:40:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天这个时候 北极星西侧的星到这个位置时...\N...when yond same star that's westward from the pole...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.78,1:40:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幽灵？\NGhost?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.92,1:40:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,钟刚好敲了一下...\N...The bell then beating one...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.14,1:40:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快住嘴 别说了\NPeace; break thee off!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.33,1:40:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看 它又现身了\NLook where it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.95,1:40:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一模一样 就像那位已故的先王\NIn the same figure, like the king that's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.72,1:40:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看 它阔步离去了\NSee, it stalks away!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.42,1:40:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他\NThat was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.44,1:40:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能告诉我 为什么...\N...Tell me why this same...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.57,1:40:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是威廉 - 嘘\N- That was Will. - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.25,1:40:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不是演员 - 不 不\N- He's not in the play. - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.70,1:40:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那幽灵就是威廉演的\NIt was Will as a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.00,1:40:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才向我们显灵的那位先王\NOur last king, Whose image but now appeared to us,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.25,1:40:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,正是那场决斗中 英勇的哈姆雷特国王...\NWas dared to the combat; our valiant Hamlet...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.22,1:40:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特\NHamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.55,1:40:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了 你听到了吗？\NDid you hear... did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.57,1:40:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.52,1:40:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们念了 念了他的名字\NThey said his-- they said his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.45,1:40:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.88,1:40:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安妮丝 别 - 让开\N- Agnes, wait. - Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.22,1:40:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,安静\NPlease be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.97,1:41:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们干嘛念他的名字啊\NWait, did they say his name? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.45,1:41:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别自找苦吃\NDo not upset yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.62,1:41:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他凭什么 凭什么喊我儿子的名字？\NWhy is-- Why did he use his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.45,1:41:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他当他谁啊 - 安静\N- I don't know him. - Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.08,1:41:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...依我之见\N...and by my advice,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.26,1:41:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不如将我们今晚所见\NLet us impart what we have seen tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.92,1:41:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,禀告给年轻的王子...\NUnto the young prince...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.14,1:41:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不许念我儿子的名字\NDon't you dare pronounce my son's name!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.69,1:41:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NQuiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.87,1:41:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...对我们沉默的幽灵 会对他说话\N...dumb to us, will speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.43,1:41:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说大家对我亲爱的王兄死讯\NThough yet of our dear brother's death,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.98,1:41:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还记忆犹新\NThe memory be green,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.43,1:41:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们要节哀顺变\NYet so far hath discretion fought with nature
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.79,1:41:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在深切缅怀他的同时\NThat we with wisest sorrow think on him,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.04,1:41:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也要为我们自身着想啊\NTogether with remembrance of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.99,1:41:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了 我不能再看下去了\NI will not stay a minute longer to be a part of this jest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.05,1:41:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别急 再看一会儿 - 我的侄儿\N- Wait. One moment. - ...my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.70,1:41:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我要回家 - 哈姆雷特\N- No. I want to go home. -  Hamlet...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.70,1:41:44.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【哈姆雷特: 原著中先王与王子同名皆为哈姆雷特】
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.02,1:41:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也是我的儿子\Nand my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.58,1:41:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还一脸愁云？\NHow is it that the clouds still hang on you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.94,1:41:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的好哈姆雷特 脱去这沉重的黑衣\NGood Hamlet, cast thy nighted color off.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.21,1:41:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别总是低眉垂眼的\NDo not for ever with thy vailed lids
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.83,1:42:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛要从尘土中寻出你高贵的父亲\NSeek for thy noble father in the dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.17,1:42:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,万物有生必有死\NAll that lives must die,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.11,1:42:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,顺其自然 谁都会踏入永恒\NPassing through nature to eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.32,1:42:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 母后 这确实是常理\NAy, madam, it is common.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.94,1:42:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我心中的郁结\NBut I have that within which passes show.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.85,1:42:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,远非这些丧服哀装所能表达\NThese are but the trappings and the suits of woe.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.96,1:42:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,固执地沉溺于哀伤\NTo persevere In obstinate condolement
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.68,1:42:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种逆天的愚行\Nis a course of impious stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.09,1:42:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是堂堂男子的悲伤\N'Tis unmanly grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.77,1:42:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是对天意的违抗\NIt shows a will most incorrect to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.95,1:42:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.70,1:42:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真想这 这沉重的肉体消融\NThis too, too solid flesh would melt,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.94,1:43:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,化为晨露消散\NThaw and resolve itself into a dew.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.91,1:43:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真想永恒的真神\NOr that the Everlasting had not fixed
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.91,1:43:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,未曾禁止自杀这罪孽\NHis canon gainst self-slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.97,1:43:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一座荒芜不治 杂草丛生\N'Tis an unweeded garden That grows to seed;
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.90,1:43:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,长满毒花恶草的花园\Nthings rank and gross in nature possess it merely.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.70,1:43:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谁曾料到啊\NThat it should come to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.19,1:43:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才死了两个月\NBut two months dead--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.43,1:43:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还没满两个月\Nnay, not so much, not two--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.04,1:43:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一位多么杰出的国王 如同太阳神\NSo excellent a king, that was to this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.04,1:43:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在这位 却像只肮脏的禽兽\NHyperion to a... a satyr.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.27,1:43:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你要领我上哪儿去？\NWhither wilt thou lead me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.29,1:43:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快说 我不跟你走\NSpeak. I'll go no further.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.02,1:43:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你父亲的灵魂\NI am thy father's spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.57,1:43:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被判在夜间游走于这大地\NDoomed for a certain term to walk the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.19,1:43:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,白天则要忍受地狱烈火的焚烧\NAnd for the day confined to fast in fires.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.87,1:43:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时辰快到了\NMy hour is almost come
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.64,1:44:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我又得回到硫磺的火焰中...\NWhen I to sulfurous and tormenting flames
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.48,1:44:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去遭受痛苦的煎熬\NMust render up myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.02,1:44:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 唉 可怜的幽灵 - 不 不要可怜我...\N- Alas, poor ghost. - No, pity me not...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.45,1:44:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要留心听着我要告诉你的话\N...but lend thy serious hearing to what I shall unfold.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.56,1:44:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听好\NList.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.34,1:44:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 啊 听好了\NList, oh, list.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.74,1:44:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你曾深爱过你的父亲\NIf thou didst ever thy father love...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.30,1:44:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.10,1:44:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢 我仿佛闻到了清晨的气息\NBut soft, methinks I scent the morning air.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.15,1:44:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我长话短说 那天我照常在花园里午睡\NBrief let me be. Sleeping within my orchard.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.91,1:44:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你叔父趁我熟睡之际偷溜进来\NUpon my secure hour, thy uncle stole
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.32,1:44:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着一瓶天杀的剧毒毒液\NWith juice of cursed hebona in a vile,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.49,1:44:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,灌入了我的耳朵\NWithin the porches of my ears did pour
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.26,1:44:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这麻风病般的毒液...\NThe leprous distillment...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.50,1:44:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,毒性之大 嗜血如仇\N...whose effect Holds such an enmity with blood of man
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.37,1:44:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它顺着血管流动得比水银还快\NThat swift as quicksilver it courses through
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.17,1:44:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,流遍全身七窍八脉\NThe natural gates and alleys of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.13,1:44:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,突然一下子\NAnd with a sudden vigor it doth posset
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.28,1:44:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就凝固了我的血...\NAnd curd, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.25,1:44:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,像卤水点豆腐一样\N...eager droppings into milk,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.99,1:44:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把我健康的血液彻底摧毁了\NThe thin and wholesome blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.14,1:45:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这样被毒害了\NSo did it mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.54,1:45:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,转眼间我全身长满了烂疮...\NA most instant tetter barked about...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.17,1:45:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如癞病般浑身长满可憎的痂皮\N...Most lazar-like, with vile and loathsome crust,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.20,1:45:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,体无完肤\NAll my smooth body.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.44,1:45:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.53,1:45:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,惨呀\NHorrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.31,1:45:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 惨啊 太惨了\NOh, horrible. Most horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.84,1:45:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你还有人性 就不要再忍了...\NIf thou hast nature in thee, bear it not...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.22,1:45:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他成了我们的儿子\NHe has swapped places with our son.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.67,1:45:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.99,1:45:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.21,1:46:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,萤 萤火虫的微光已经暗淡\NThe... the glowworm shows the matin to be near,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.91,1:46:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明就要来了\NAnd 'gins to pale his uneffectual fires.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.13,1:46:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\NMy boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.41,1:47:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了\NAdieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.13,1:47:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了\NAdieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.48,1:47:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了\NAdieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.76,1:47:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,记着我\NRemember me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.54,1:48:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,生存还是毁灭\NTo be, or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.70,1:48:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个问题\Nthat is the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.51,1:48:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种更高贵？是默然忍受\NWhether 'tis nobler in the mind to suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.65,1:48:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,命运投来的巨石 射来的毒箭？\NThe slings and arrows of outrageous fortune,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.62,1:48:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还是挺身反抗无涯的苦海\NOr to take arms against a sea of troubles
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.08,1:48:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,通过斗争 渡向彼岸？\NAnd, by opposing, end them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.53,1:48:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,死了 沉睡了\NTo die, to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.25,1:48:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样了\NNo more.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.70,1:49:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要是一场睡眠可以终结\NAnd by a sleep, to say we end
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.95,1:49:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这些血肉之躯生来要承受的\NThe heartache and the thousand natural shocks
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.36,1:49:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,万千苦难 那可是天大的好事\NThat flesh is heir to-- 'tis a consummation
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.81,1:49:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是求之不得的结局\NDevoutly to be wished.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.34,1:49:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\NTo die,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.62,1:49:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沉睡了 没准还有梦呢\NTo sleep, perchance to dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.46,1:49:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这就是问题\NAy, there's the rub.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.74,1:49:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,摆脱了这凡尘肉体 在那死亡的沉睡中\NFor in that sleep of death, what dreams may come
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.34,1:49:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会做什么梦\NWhen we have shuffled off this mortal coil
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.14,1:49:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这必然令人踌躇\NMust give us pause.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.03,1:49:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,正是这份顾虑\NThere's the respect
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.25,1:49:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们心甘陷入这漫长的苦难\NThat makes calamity of so long life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.44,1:49:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁甘心忍受这人世的鞭挞和嘲辱\NWho would bear the whips and scorns of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.42,1:49:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,压迫的屈辱\NThe oppressor's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.75,1:49:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢的蔑辱\Nthe proud man's contumely,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.25,1:49:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,心碎的羞辱\NThe pangs of despised love,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.35,1:49:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,法律的冷辱\Nthe law's delay,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.67,1:49:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,官吏的欺辱 以及小人对\NThe insolence of office, and the spurns
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.59,1:49:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,勤勤恳恳老实人的侮辱\NThat patient merit of the unworthy take,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.84,1:49:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,否则当一把匕首就能解脱\NWhen he himself might his quietus make
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.85,1:49:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁不愿意？\NWith a bare bodkin?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.42,1:49:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谁愿背负这重担\NWho would fardels bear,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.99,1:49:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,撑着这疲惫的身躯呻吟 流汗\NTo grunt and sweat under a weary life,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.42,1:49:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是死后那无人归返\NBut that the dread of something after death,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.27,1:49:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,未知的国度令我们恐惧\NThe undiscovered country from whose bourn
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.55,1:49:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,困扰了我们的意志\NNo traveler returns, puzzles the will,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.71,1:50:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,使我们宁愿忍受眼前的不幸...\NAnd makes us rather bear those ills...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.44,1:50:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位\NEn garde!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.64,1:50:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一剑\NOne!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.67,1:50:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没有击中\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.11,1:50:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,中了 很明显的一剑\NA hit, a palpable hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.30,1:50:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子一定会胜利\NOur son shall win!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.70,1:50:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 再来 - 格特鲁德 别喝\N- Well, again! - Gertrude, do not drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.29,1:51:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一剑 你自己说中没中\NAnother hit! What say you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.44,1:51:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我一剑\NHave at you now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.85,1:51:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,王后怎么了？\NHow does the queen?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.19,1:51:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定是看见流血晕倒了\NShe swoons to see them bleed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.93,1:52:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 是那酒 那酒\NNo, no, the drink, the drink!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.46,1:52:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我心爱的哈姆雷特\NOh, my dear Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.55,1:52:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我中毒了\NI am poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.32,1:52:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 恶毒的阴谋\NOh, villainy!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.80,1:52:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 把门锁上\NHo, let the door be locked!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.68,1:52:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,奸贼 揪出来\NTreachery! Seek it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.73,1:52:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特 奸贼就在这儿\NIt is here, Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.48,1:52:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特 你也要死了\NHamlet, thou art slain.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.30,1:52:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有药能救得了你\NNo medicine in the world can do thee good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.75,1:52:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你活不到半个钟头了\NIn thee, there is not half an hour's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.67,1:52:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都是国王做的孽\NThe king's to blame!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.09,1:52:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,剑头也有毒药？\NThe point envenomed, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.95,1:52:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么好 毒药 也给你\NThen, venom, to thy work!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.86,1:52:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个乱伦的 血腥的丹麦的魔王\NHere, thou incestuous, murderous, damned Dane!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.27,1:52:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,给我喝...\NDrink...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.89,1:52:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下这杯毒酒\NDrink off this potion!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.28,1:53:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你那心爱的珍珠在里面吗？\NIs thy union here?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.28,1:53:02.84,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【心爱的珍珠: "union"具双关 既指原著中的珍珠 又指婚姻】
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.86,1:53:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我的母亲一道去吧\NFollow my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.96,1:53:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了\NI am dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.84,1:53:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可你还活着\NThou livest.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.68,1:53:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请将我的故事与大义\NReport me and my cause aright
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.77,1:53:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如实告知尚不知情的人吧\NTo the unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.86,1:53:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,若你曾对我怀有深情与敬重\NIf thou didst ever hold me in thy heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.98,1:53:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,暂且别去享那极乐\NAbsent thee from felicity awhile,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.24,1:53:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,留在这残酷的尘世 隐忍着痛苦\NAnd in this harsh world draw thy breath in pain
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.34,1:53:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去把我的故事讲清\NTo tell my story.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.34,1:54:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我要死了\NAh, I die!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.17,1:54:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这剧毒正夺去我的意志\NThe potent poison quite o'ercrows my spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.89,1:55:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,余下的只有沉寂\NThe rest is silence.
